    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a class containing over 1,000,000 species characerized by a body divided into head, thorax, and abdomen; head with one pair of antennae, mouthparts consisting of a pair of mandibles and two pairs of maxillae, several pairs of legs, and often wings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
